**COMPANY & BUSINESS**

**OVERVIEW**

ADT is the leading U.S. provider of residential and small business
security monitoring services, serving approximately 6.4 million
customers. The company generates revenue primarily through multi-year
monitoring contracts with recurring monthly revenue (RMR) of
\~\$362M/month. ADT operates a vertically integrated model including
equipment sales, professional installation, and 24/7 monitoring
services.

**STRATEGIC EVOLUTION**

**Commercial Business:** Divested October 2023 - focus on core
residential

**Solar Business:** Exited 2024 - underperformed expectations, 73
employees laid off (July 2024)

**Multifamily Business:** Divested October 2025 (\~200K customers,
\$2.6M RMR)

**Strategic Partners:** Google (\$450M investment, 2020) + State Farm
(\$1.2B investment, 2022)

**CONCENTRATION ANALYSIS**

**Customer:** LOW - 6.4M subscribers, no single customer \>1%

**Geographic:** MODERATE - primarily U.S. residential markets

**Product:** LOW - diversified security/automation offerings

**Supplier:** LOW - multiple equipment suppliers

